msgstr "Kêk"

msgid "With 7 tasty slices!"
msgstr ""

msgid "Hunger points: +@1 per slice"
msgstr ""

msgid "Cakes can be placed and eaten to restore hunger points. A cake has 7 slices. Each slice restores 2 hunger points and 0.4 saturation points. Cakes will be destroyed when dug or when the block below them is broken."
msgstr ""

msgid "Place the cake anywhere, then rightclick it to eat a single slice. You can't eat from the cake when your hunger bar is full."
